      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "@1440000bytes: The likelihood of a situation arising in which this is relevant is so minuscule that performing the additional computation step is not justified, especially since it would only cause the transaction to revert to unconfirmed unless we are the target of a Finney attack. If we are the target of a Finney attack, the result is that we didn't get paid in the first place and we would have to redo the subsequent payment once the dust settles.",
